# Release v0.3.0

## What's New
- Sprint 3 documentation
- Frontend (React + TypeScript) with Login, Dashboard, Cloud and AI Agent pages
- AI agent for campaign analysis via natural language (LangGraph + FastAPI)
- Kubernetes hardening: Liveness/Readiness Probes, Security Contexts, RBAC
- CSV Kafka Producer: health checks, Prometheus metrics, precise rate control
- GCP infrastructure with Terraform: IAM, separated Dev/Prod environments
